<li><strong>Personalized decor</strong>: Infuse your wedding with your unique style and personality. Our rooms are a blank canvas waiting for your creative touch. From floral arrangements to lighting, make it truly yours.&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Culinary excellence</strong>: Meet Tulips and Maple, our esteemed onsite caterer. Renowned for their culinary prowess, they’ll craft custom menus tailored to your preferences. Expect an unforgettable dining experience that delights the senses.&nbsp;</li>
